description: France has announced that it is sending several artillery weapons including CAESAR howitzers to Ukraine. The announcement comes after Zelensky made repeated requests to the West  to provide heavier weapons to fight Russia. title: Ukraine war: Drone footage shows aftermath of Ukraine helicopter strike
description: The Ukrainian National Guard released footage of what it said was the aftermath of its forces shooting down a Russian helicopter on April 21.|The video shows a fire among fields as a second helicopter releases flares in an apparent attempt to avoid being targeted. description: ===|||| GRESIK, KOMPAS.TV - Ada pemandangan unik saat Presiden Joko Widodo (Jokowi) melakukan kunjungan kerja di Gresik, Jawa Timur, Rabu (20/4).||||Saat rombongan melintas kerumunan warga, orang nomor satu Indonesia tersebut menjadi pusat perhatian warga yang sudah menunggunya.||||Jokowi yang mengenakan kemeja putih dan celana hitam denga sepatu kets tersebut pun dipanggil-panggil warga.||||Pada momen itu, ada yang menggelitik dalam video tersebut.||||Terdengar teriakan suara anak kecil seperti nada menyindir.||||"Yo ndak tahu kok tanya saya," ucap seorang anak kecil secara tiba-tiba seperti diunggah melalui Instagram majeliskopi08.||||"Lho ya ndak tahu."||||"Yo ndak tahu Pak"||||Namun teriakan anak kecil itu tak berlangsung lama, lantaran saat melewati sejumlah warga yang berada di seberang Jokowi itu terdengar memuji pemimpin Indonesia tersebut.||||"Pak! Pak Jokowi! Pakdhe!" panggil warga yang menyambut kedatagan Jokowi.||||Lantaran potongan video tersebut, sejumlah warganet pun mengomentari celetukkan suara bocah yang terdengar dalam video tersebut.||||Video Editor: Febi Ramdani||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/282384/viral-bocah-bocah-teriak-yo-ndak-tahu-kok-tanya-saya-saat-sambut-kunjungan-jokowi-ke-gresik

title: Zelenskyy Thanks Partners for â€˜Finallyâ€™ Providing the Weapons Ukraine Needs
description: Russiaâ€™s deputy military commander said Moscow's goal is to control Donbas and southern Ukraine, which would give Russia access the separatist Moldovan enclave of Transnistria and block Kyivâ€™s access to the Black Sea. But U.S. officials vow to help Ukraine defend itself, as VOAâ€™s Senior Diplomatic Correspondent Cindy Saine reports.|As Russiaâ€™s assault on Ukraine continues in the city of Kharkiv, U.S. Secretary of State Antony Blinken welcomed Ukraine Prime Minister Denys Shmyhal to the State Department Friday. Blinken again expressed confidence that Ukraine will prevail in the war.|Antony Blinken, Secretary of State:|"I think this is the first visit since the Russian aggression by a senior official of the Ukrainian government, further evidence that an independent, sovereign Ukraine is going to be around a lot longer than Vladimir Putin.â€|Both Prime Minister Shmyhal and Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy thanked the U.S. and other Western partners for â€œfinallyâ€ providing the weapons Ukraine needs to fight back against Russiaâ€™s offensive in Donbas and southern Ukraine.|Volodymyr Zelenskyy, Ukrainian President:|â€œAnd I am grateful to all our partners who finally heard us, who are providing us with exactly what we asked for. Because we know for sure that with these weapons, we will be able to save the lives of thousands of people."|At the Pentagon, press secretary John Kirby was asked whether Ukraine's forces, now that they're getting heavy weapons, would be able to beat back the invading Russians.|John Kirby, Pentagon Press Secretary|â€œI think that's a question that only the Ukrainian armed forces can answer, not the United States military. What I can tell you is that we, in keeping with another 30 plus nations, are doing everything we can to give them the tools that they need to defend themselves and to push the Russians out. â€œ|Some observers say the U.S. assessment of Ukraineâ€™s ability to win has shifted over the past couple of weeks.|Anne Applebaum, Historian:|"Until the last week or so, I think Americans still weren't wholly convinced that Ukraine could win. title: Charlo vs Hatley FULL FIGHT: April 22, 2017 | PBC on Showtime
description: (April 22, 2017) Jermell Charlo capped a powerful performance with a sixth-round KO of Charles Hatley to retain his 154-pound world title.|Jermell Charlo vowed that he would have a breakthrough performance in his first 154-pound title defense, and he backed up that promise with a devastating knockout of Charles Hatley.|Charlo dropped Hatley in the third round before finishing him off in the sixth to retain his world championship at Barclays Center.|The knockout was sensational as Charlo punctuated a barrage of blows with a head-swiveling right hand that landed as Hatley missed with a left. The challenger fell face-first to the canvas and was out cold beneath the bottom rope on the ring apron as referee Harvey Dock immediately waved an end to the fight 32 seconds into Round 6.|Charlo, 26, showed more power than he had in previous fights as he put the rest of the 154-pound division on notice, and looked forward to a possible title unification against recently crowned champion Jarrett Hurd, who earned the title that Charloâ€™s twin brother, Jermall, vacated earlier this year to move up to 160.|Jermell Charlo defended his title for the first time since earning the vacant championship last May with an eighth-round KO over John Jackson in Las Vegas. He made history that night by joining Jermall as the first siblings to simultaneously hold 154-pound world titles.|Hatley lost for the first time since being stopped by Lanardo Tyner in the first round in August 2012.|The 31-year-old Dallas native had some success early against Charlo, but the champion staggered him against the ropes at the end of Round 2. Charlo totally seized control in Round 3, when Hatley was floored for the seventh time in his career with a right to the temple.|After Hatley was warned for an intentional headbutt in the fourth, Charlo stunned him with a stiff jab and later with a right just before the end of the round.|#JermellCharlo #CharlesHatley #CharloHatley|Visit PremierBoxingChampions.com for more info.||||SIGN UP FOR FIGHT ALERTS: ||||https://pbcham.ps/FightAlerts||||FOLLOW US:||||https://twitter.com/premierboxing||https://instagram.com/premierboxing||https://www.facebook.com/premierboxingchampions

title: Detroit man set to walk free from prison until officer brought exoneration hearing to halt
description: Family who traveled to Southeast Michigan to celebrate the release of a man imprisoned for someone elseâ€™s crimes said they were shocked and saddened to find the hearing was delayed. The case dates back to 2006, when someone sexually assaulted a 13-year-old girl and attempted to assault a 15-year-old girl near a liquor store on Fenkell Avenue in Detroit. Both girls picked Terance Calhoun out of separate lineups. In 2007, Calhoun pleaded no contest to charges including first-degree criminal sexual conduct and kidnapping. A no-contest plea is a plea by which a defendant accepts conviction, but does not plead or admit guilt.

title: Feid: Tiny Desk (Home) Concert
description: The Tiny Desk is working from home for the foreseeable future. Introducing NPR Music's Tiny Desk (home) concerts, bringing you performances from across the country and the world. It's the same spirit â€” stripped-down sets, an intimate setting â€” just a different space.|Anamaria Sayre | April 22, 2022|From the line up of traditional Colombian instruments to the card playing interlude, every second of Feid's MedellÃ­n, Colombia pool hall performance invokes the feeling of charlando and cantando, chatting and singing, with friends.|Seamlessly anchoring all five tracks with a bass-emulating acoustic guitar and cajÃ³n-driven dembow, the new guard reggaeton royal brings unique instrumentation and culturally significant visuals to this Tiny Desk (home) concert for a deeply authentic portrait of a star on the rise baring a sonic piece of his soul to the world.|Flexing his multi-instrumentalist background, Feid brings in a new instrument for each arrangement of his hit tracks to represent the five different regions of Colombia in a comprehensive homage to his home. He opens with su propio region, using a tiple guitar from the Andean region on "JORDAN IV." Moving to the Llanos, his band breaks out a harp for a beautiful rendition of "TE MATA." He pulls in a tambor alegre on "VACAXIONES" to represent cumbia from the Caribbean region. Pausing for quick brindis, taking a shot, he closes out the show with two heartfelt numbers: First, an accordion-backed, vallenato version of "AMOR DE MI VIDA" for the Atlantic coastal region, and then a final pivot to the Pacific coastal region he mixes in a marimba de chonta on "SI TÃš SUPIERAS," before leaving the hall and riding off on a motorcycle.|The Colombian artist utilizes his full 15-minute set to depict an artistic and intentional musical image of his home and its rich sonic diversity, bringing the people, place and spirit behind a global genre center stage.|SET LIST|"JORDAN IV"|"TE MATA"|"VACAXIONES"|"AMOR DE MI VIDA"|"SI TÃš SUPIERAS"|MUSICIANS|Feid: vocals|Pedro MejÃ­a: Music Director, guitar|NicolÃ¡s Guevara: cajÃ³n|Angel "Arpangel" Rodriguez: harp|Daniel Uribe: tiple|Mateo Morales: tambor alegre |Kike Riascos: marimba|Luis Javier Hernandez: accordion|CREDITS|Director: Sebastian SÃ¡nchez |Executive Producer: Feid, SebastiÃ¡n Arango|Project Manager: Albert Piedrahita|Production Coordinator: Fernando RÃ­os|Personal Manager: Luis Villamizar|Assistant Director: Ana Isabel Duque|Director of Photography: unmojigato|Audio Engineer: Miguel Mass|Assistant Audio: Estefania Giraldo|1st AC: Camilo Gutierrez|2st AC: Lukas Restrepo|Ronin: SebastiÃ¡n Escobar Gil|VHS Camera: Felipe Molina|DIT: Santiago Arango|Gaffer: JuliÃ¡n EchavarrÃ­a|Lighting Engineer: Carlos BeltrÃ¡n|Electric: Nilson Florez|Assistant Lights: Jhonatan Satizabal, Arnulfo Villada|Production Design: Camila Agudelo|Assistant Art: Elizabeth RendÃ³n, John Esteban Isaza|TINY DESK TEAM|Producer: Anamaria Sayre|Video Producer: Michael Zamora|Audio Mastering: Josh Rogosin|Tiny Production Team: Bob Boilen, Bobby Carter, Kara Frame, Joshua Bryant, Maia Stern, Ashley Pointer|Executive Producer: Keith Jenkins|Senior VP, Programming: Anya Grundmann

title: Red Hot Monaco ties the series! | Playoffs Game 2, Highlights | Turkish Airlines EuroLeague
description: AS Monaco produced a brilliant performance at both ends of the court to down Olympiacos Piraeus 72-96, tying the series at one game apiece. |ABOUT EUROLEAGUE BASKETBALL |Euroleague Basketball (EB) is a global leader in the sports and entertainment business, devoted to running the top European competitions of professional basketball clubs under a unique and innovative organizational model. Owned and administered by some of the most successful and historic clubs in the world, EB manages the continentâ€™s two premier menâ€™s basketball competitions, the Turkish Airlines EuroLeague and the 7DAYS EuroCup, as well as the sportâ€™s premier under-18 showcase, the EB Adidas Next Generation Tournament.|The EB competitions bring the elite of European basketball to all five continents and to the entire sports community through the OTT platform EuroLeague TV. EB also organizes a series of community and educational activities, led by the One Team program, in alignment with the United Nations Agenda 2030 Sustainable Development Goals. On the academic side, the EB Sports Business MBA trains future professionals in sports management.|About One Team|One Team, Euroleague Basketball's corporate social responsibility (CSR) program , supported by Turkish Airlines as the One Team Founding Patron and with the collaboration of Special Olympics as Proud Partner, uses basketball to achieve real social impact in our communities. With an innovative model of interconnectedness across an entire continent, Euroleague Basketball and its clubs have developed a complete CSR program that brings together activities from each team in an integrated, impactful way, working under the theme of "community integration" that actively addresses targets of the United Nations Sustainable Development Goal 10 on Reduced Inequalities. Each participating club develops a specific One Team project tailored to its own community needs to benefit groups in danger of exclusion due to problems such as substance abuse and gender, physical or intellectual disability. Since its founding in 2012, the One Team program has reached already directly and indirectly more than 23,000 participants through its various team projects.

title: The history of the Red Army (2/2) | DW Documentary
description: After the Second World War ended, the glory of the Red Army waned. Then, as the Cold War raged, Khrushchev burnished the armyâ€™s reputation once more. But from then on, the army had a purely repressive function.|After World War II, the Red Armyâ€™s activities were primarily directed against popular uprisings in the USSR's sphere of influence. These were brutally put down. Today, the Red Army is primarily a symbol of nostalgic nationalist aspirations. |Following the victory over fascism in the summer of 1945, nine million Soviet soldiers returned home. But prisoners of war who had survived the German camps were often accused of treason when they finally reached their motherland, and sent to gulags. Others were forced to beg, as their war pensions were cut, or found themselves banished from major cities. Stalin had decided to put an end to the glorious days of the Red Army, after the victory against Hitler's Germany. As the Cold War began, the Red Armyâ€˜s only function was to maintain public order and security. |But after Stalin's death in 1953, the cards were reshuffled. The new strongman Nikita Khrushchev had gotten rid of his rival, interior ministry chief Lavrenti Beria, with the help of the Red Army. After taking power, Khrushchev initiated a program of de-Stalinization. He appointed Marshal Georgi Zhukov, who had fallen out of favor with Stalin, as defense minister. Khrushchev then reorganized and modernized the Red Army. He restored its prestige and reintroduced a pension for wartime service. |With the support of Soviet tanks, the Red Army was instrumental in bloodily crushing the uprisings in Poland and Budapest in 1956 and in Prague in 1968. And they played a role in the ongoing Cold War battles being waged with the West. |By the 1970s, the living conditions of Red Army soldiers had deteriorated drastically. Many conscripts tried to avoid military service. But there was often no escape from the nightmarish mission in Afghanistan. The Red Army was increasingly weakened and demoralized as dislike for the Soviet system grew. In 1989, ten years after the conflict in Afghanistan began, President Mikhail Gorbachev ordered the Red Army to withdraw from that country and bring its soldiers home. This defeat played a role in the disintegration of the USSR, which took place in the wake of Gorbachevâ€™s resignation on December 25, 1991.|#documentary #dwdocumentary |______|DW Documentary gives you knowledge beyond the headlines. title: Kremlin reveals its goal for 'second phase' of Ukraine invasion
description: Russia has revealed that the goal of its invasion of Ukraine is to take "full control" over southern Ukraine as well as the eastern Donbas region. The announcement by a top military official marks the first time Russia admitted it was fighting to establish a land corridor through Ukrainian territory connecting Russia to Crimea, the peninsula it annexed in 2014. "Since the beginning of the second phase of the special operation, which began literally two days ago, one of the tasks of the Russian army is to establish full control over Donbas and southern Ukraine. This will provide a land corridor to Crimea," Maj. Gen. Rustam Minnekaev, the acting commander of Russia's Central Military District, said according to TASS, a Russian state news agency. #CNN #News

title: Korupsi Ekspor Minyak Goreng, Kejagung Periksa Mendag?
description: KOMPAS.TV - Pasca penetapan 4 orang tersangka kasus dugaan korupsi pemberian izin ekspor minyak sawit mentah atau CPO, penyidik Jaksa Agung Muda Bidang Tindak Pidana Khusus Kejaksaan Agung memeriksa 30 saksi terkait dugaan korupsi pemberian izin ekspor produk CPO.||||Tapi, nama Menteri Perdagangan M Luthfi, Belum masuk dalam daftar pemanggilan saksi.||||Hal itu disampaikan oleh Jaksa Agung Muda Tindak Pidana Khusus Febri Adriansyah, pada Jumat siang yang memastikan nama menteri perdagangan belum akan dipanggil sebagai saksi, meskipun salah satu dari 4 tersangka adalah dirjen perdagangan luar negeri kementerian perdagangan.||||Baca Juga Kejagung Ungkap Peran Dirjen Kemendag Soal Korupsi Minyak Goreng di https://www.kompas.tv/article/282507/kejagung-ungkap-peran-dirjen-kemendag-soal-korupsi-minyak-goreng||||Jampidsus membeberkan tersangka Dirjen Perdagangan Luar Negeri Indrasari Wishnu Wardana memberikan izin ekspor kepada produsen CPO yang tak memenuhi syarat domestik market obligation atau DMO sebesar 30 persen dan 20 persen dari total jumlah ekspor.||||Sementara itu hari ini (2/04) 2organisasi sipil beranggotakan Sawit Watch, elSAM, HuMa, PILNET, WALHI, hingga Greenpeace Indonesia mendatangi kementerian perdagangan untuk memberikan somasi kepada sejumlah lembaga negara mulai dari presiden Joko Widodo, Menko Perekonomian Airlangga Hartarto, Menteri Perdagangan M Lutfi, dan Menteri Perindustrian Agus Gumiwang.||||Mereka meminta agar pemerintah prioritaskan kebutuhan minyak goreng dalam negeri ketimbang ekspor serta menetapkan kembali harga eceran tertinggi ditingkat peritel.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/282531/korupsi-ekspor-minyak-goreng-kejagung-periksa-mendag

title: Large hadron collider upgrade 'revolutionary' - BBC News
description: The large hadron collider, the world's most advanced particle accelerator, has undergone a major revamp which scientists say could spark a physics revolution.|The vast machine, deep underground in the Swiss Alps, smashes atoms together to break them apart and discover what is inside them.|Since the upgrade, its instruments are more sensitive, allowing researchers to study the collision of particles from the inside of atoms in higher definition.|It means there's now the best chance ever of the machine finding subatomic particles that are completely new to science. |The hope is that it will make discoveries that will spark the biggest revolution in physics in a hundred years.|The BBC's science correspondent Pallab Ghosh reports.|Please subscribe HERE http://bit.ly/1rbfUog|#Switzerland #BBCNews

title: 'Personal Visit': U.S on Ilhan Omar's PoK visit after strong condemnation by India
description: US lawmaker Ilhan Omar's meeting with recently ousted Pakistani Prime Minister Imran Khan and her "unofficial, personal" visit to Pakistan Occupied Kashmir (PoK) did not represent the United States government in any way, an official said. India had on Thursday condemned Omar's visit to PoK as violative of India's territorial integrity and sovereignty and that it reflected her "narrow-minded" politics. The Democratic Congresswoman is on a four-day visit to Pakistan that began on April 20. On Wednesday, she met Imran Khan as well as visited a part of PoK. title: Tim Resmob Polresta Solo Tembak Anggota Polsek Slogoghimo yang Jadi Otak Pemerasan di Surakarta!
description: SURAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Anggota Polsek Slogoghimo ditembak Tim Resmob Polresta Solo lantaran menjadi otak kasus pemerasan di Surakarta.||||Tersangka bersama empat rekannya, menjebak para korban dengan tuduhan melakukan perselingkuhan di sebuah hotel dan meminta sejumlah uang kepada korban.||||Anggota Polsek Slogohimo Polres Wonogiri, Jawa Tengah, dalam kondisi kritis setelah ditembak oleh Tim Resmob Polresta Solo di Sukoharjo.||||Polisi menangkap empat orang rekan tersangka dan menyita barang bukti mobil, senjata api rakitan dan uang hasil pemerasan.||||Dari laporan yang diterima, polisi mengungkap komplotan pemerasan ini telah melakukan 15 aksi di sejumlah lokasi di Solo, Boyolali, dan Semarang.||||Tersangka masih menjalani perawatan akibat luka tembak dibagian perut di rumah sakit di Kota Solo.||||Kasus dugaan pemerasan ini terus diselidiki polisi, diduga masih ada korban lain namun tidak berani melapor karena takut perselingkuhannya terbongkar.||||_____                             ||||Jangan lewatkan live streaming Kompas TV 24 jam nonstop di https://www.kompas.tv/live.||||Agar tidak ketinggalan berita-berita terkini, terlengkap, serta laporan langsung dari berbagai daerah di Indonesia. title: Kata Kapolresta Bogor Terkait Pedagang Mengadu ke Jokowi Saudaranya Ditangkap karena Lawan Pungli
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Kapolresta Bogor tindak lanjuti soal pedagang yang mengadu ke Presiden Joko Widodo saat kunjungi Pasar Bogor pada Kamis (21/4)||||Diketahui, kedua pedagang tersebut mengadu ke Jokowi saudaranya ditangkap polisi karena menolak pungli.||||Kombes Susatyo Purnomo menjelaskan bahwa kasus yang menimpa saudara para pedagang tersebut yakni Ujang Sarjana bukan terlibat dalam kasus pungli melainkan terlibat adlam kasus pengeroyokan dan saat ini sudah dalam proses persidangan.||||Saat menyampaikan informasi ini, polisi juga menghadirkan dua orang pedagang yang menjadi korban pengeroyokan Ujang Sarjana, yakni Agus Susanto alias Komeng dan Andriansyah.||||Baca Juga Tangis Histeris Pedagang di Bogor Adukan ke Jokowi, Pamannya Ditangkap Polisi karena Tolak Pungli di https://www.kompas.tv/article/282349/tangis-histeris-pedagang-di-bogor-adukan-ke-jokowi-pamannya-ditangkap-polisi-karena-tolak-pungli||||Sementara kasus Ujang Sarjana sendiri saat ini sudah dalam proses persidangan dengan agenda putusan sela.||||Sementara itu, Wali Kota Bogor Bima Arya membantah adanya pungli di pasar Bogor. Ia menegaskan apabila terbukti ada praktek pungli dan ada ASN yang terlibat akan dilakukan tindakan tegas.||||Bima juga berharap adanya partisipasi warga untuk melaporkan apabila menemukan pungutan liar.||||Video Editor: Ian Andrian||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/282461/kata-kapolresta-bogor-terkait-pedagang-mengadu-ke-jokowi-saudaranya-ditangkap-karena-lawan-pungli

title: Ukraine: Satellite images suggest mass graves near Mariupol | DW News
description: Imagery released by the Maxar Technologies showed what appeared to be long rows of graves stretching away from an existing cemetery in the town of Manhush, outside Mariupol.|The images showed graves aligned in four sections of linear rows measuring approximately 85 meters (around 279 feet) per section and containing more than 200 graves. |Mariupol Mayor Vadym Boychenko accused Russian forces of "hiding their military crimes" by taking the bodies of civilians from the city and burying them in Manhush. According to Boychenko, as many as 9,000 civilians could be buried at the site.|On Thursday Russian President Vladimir Putin claimed victory in the battle for Mariupol, despite the presence of an estimated 2,000 Ukrainian fighters who were still holed up at a giant steel mill. description: We have perfected the art of making chili bites and this time this Dynamite Chilli bites recipe comes with a trick to perfectly crumb coat the chili bies each time. #HappyCookingToYou #FoodFusion #7up|Written Recipe: https://bit.ly/36CjeIl|Dynamite Chilli Bites|Recipe in English:|Ingredients:|Prepare Chilli Bites:|-Boneless chicken cubes 200g|-Soy sauce 1 tbs|-Sirka (Vinegar) Â½ tbs|-Paprika powder 1 tsp|-Dried oregano Â½ tsp|-Namak (Salt) Â½ tsp or to taste |-Lal mirch powder (Red chilli powder) Â½ tsp or to taste |-Lehsan paste (Garlic paste) 1 tsp|-Cooking oil 1-2 tbs|-Mozzarella cheese 100g|-Cheddar cheese 100g|-Green chillies or Jalapenos as required|-Maida (All-purpose flour) 1 Cup|-Anday (Eggs) whisked 2-3|-Breadcrumbs 1 Cup or as required|-Cooking oil for frying |Prepare Dynamite Sauce:|-Mayonnaise Â¾ Cup|-Tomato ketchup 3 tbs|-Chilli sauce 3-4 tbs|-Honey 1 tbs|-Lehsan powder (Garlic powder) Â½ tsp|Directions:|Prepare Chilli Bites:|-In a frying pan,add chicken,soy sauce,vinegar,paprika powder,dried oregano,salt,red chilli powder, garlic paste and mix well.|-Add cooking oil,cover & marinate for 15 minutes.|-Turn on the flame & cook on medium flame until chicken is tender & dries up.|-Let it cool.|-In a chopper,add chicken & chop well.|-Take out in a bowl,add mozzarella cheese,cheddar cheese,mix well & set aside.|-Slit green chillies with the help of knife & deseed them.|-Stuffed green chillies with prepared filling,coat in all-purpose flour then dip in whisked eggs and coat well with breadcrumbs and again dip in whisked eggs & coat with breadcrumbs & let them rest for 10 minutes (makes 45-50). |-Can be stored for up to 2 weeks in freezer. |Option # 1: Deep Fry|-In a wok,heat cooking oil (170-180C) & fry stuffed chillies on medium high flame until golden & crispy.|Option # 2: Air Fry|-Spray non-stick spray on both sides of chillies & air fry at 180C for 10-12 minutes.|Prepare Dynamite Sauce:|-In a bowl,add mayonnaise,tomato ketchup,chilli sauce,honey & garlic powder,whisk well & transfer to a squeeze bottle.|-Drizzle dynamite sauce on chilli bites & serve with 7Up!|Recipe in Urdu:|Ajza:|Prepare Chilli Bites:|-Boneless chicken cubes 200g|-Soy sauce 1 tbs|-Sirka (Vinegar) Â½ tbs|-Paprika powder 1 tsp|-Dried oregano Â½ tsp|-Namak (Salt) Â½ tsp or to taste |-Lal mirch powder (Red chilli powder) Â½ tsp or to taste |-Lehsan paste (Garlic paste) 1 tsp|-Cooking oil 1-2 tbs|-Mozzarella cheese 100g|-Cheddar cheese 100g|-Green chillies or Jalapenos as required|-Maida (All-purpose flour) 1 Cup|-Anday (Eggs) whisked 2-3|-Breadcrumbs 1 Cup or as required|-Cooking oil for frying |Prepare Dynamite Sauce:|-Mayonnaise Â¾ Cup|-Tomato ketchup 3 tbs|-Chilli sauce 3-4 tbs|-Honey 1 tbs|-Lehsan powder (Garlic powder) Â½ tsp|Directions:|Prepare Chilli Bites:|-Frying pan mein chicken,soy sauce,sirka,paprika powder,dried oregano,lal mirch powder aur lehsan paste dal ker ache tarhan mix ker lein.|-Cooking oil dal ker dhak dein aur 15 minutes kliya marinate ker lein.|-Chulha on karein aaur darmiyani ancch per chicken gul & sukh janay tak paka lein.|-Thanda ker lein.|-Chopper mein chicken dal ker ache tarhan chop ker lein.|-Bowl mein nikal lein,mozzarella cheese & cheddar cheese dal ker ache tarhan mix ker lein.|-Hari mirch ko knife ki madad sa slit laga lein aur seeds ko nikal lein.|-Tayyar filling ko hari mirchon mein bhar dein,maida mein caot karein phir pheetay hoye anday mein dip karein aur breadcrumbs mein coat ker lein phir dubara pheetay hoye anday mein dip karein aur breadcrumbs mein coat ker lein aur 10 minues kliya rest dein (makes 45-50). |-2 weeks kliya freezer mein store ker saktay han.|Option # 1: Deep Fry|-Karahi mein cooking oil garam karein (170-180C) & stuffed chillies ko darmiyani tez ancch per golden & crispy ho janay tak fry ker lein.|Option # 2: Air Fry|-Chillies ki dono sides per non-stick spray karein aur 180C per 10-12 minutes kliya air fry ker lein.|Prepare Dynamite Sauce:|-Bowl mein mayonnaise,tomato ketchup,chilli sauce,shahad & lehsan powder dal ker ache tarhan whisk ker lein aur squeeze bottle mein dal dein.|-Dynamite sauce ko chilli bites mein drizzle ker ka 7up ka saath serve karein!

title: Boris Johnson lauds PM Modi for warm welcome as UK premier arrives in Delhi; 'Absolutely fantastic'
description: Prime Minister Narendra Modi on Friday received UK Prime Minister Boris Johnson with a ceremonial reception at Rashtrapati Bhawan in New Delhi. title: Keluar PSI karena Suaminya Pendukung Anies Baswedan? Tsamara Amany Menjawab...
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Tsamara Amany memberikan klarifikasinya soal ramai beredar alasan ia keluar dari Partai Solidaritas Indonesia karena suaminya, Ismail Fajrie Alatas, teman dekat dari Gubernur DKI Jakarta Anies Baswedan.||||Diketahui, PSI kerap melontarkan kritik kepada Anies Baswedan terkait sejumlah kebijakannya.||||Meski demikian, Tsamara tak memungkiri bahwa pernah memberikan apresiasi kepada Pemprov DKI Jakarta dan Anies Baswedan dalam penanganan Covid-19 di Jakarta.||||Baca Juga Ramai soal Cuitan Suami Dukung Anies Baswedan, Tsamara Amany Beri Respons Menohok! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/282353/ramai-soal-cuitan-suami-dukung-anies-baswedan-tsamara-amany-beri-respons-menohok||||"Jadi aku mau tanya konfirmasi dari Tsamara Amany, bener enggak kamu keluar dari PSI itu karena Prof Ajie, suamimu, itu pendukungnya Gubernur Anies Baswedan?" tanya Rosianna Silalahi dalam program Kamar Rosi yang tayang di YouTube KompasTV pada Kamis (21/4/2022).||||"Sudah pasti enggak," jawab Tsamara.||||"Sebenarnya kalau mau jujur, kita semua nothing personal kalau misalnya di dalam politik ini. Kalau aku mengkritik Pak Anies itu nothing personal gitu, itu kritik aja, kritik secara substantif, kritik secara objektif aja," lanjut Tsamara.||||Tsamara pun mengungkapkan bahwa ia sudah tahu dari dulu bahwa suaminya memang teman dekat Anies Baswedan.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/282371/keluar-psi-karena-suaminya-pendukung-anies-baswedan-tsamara-amany-menjawab

title: Royal Fruit Falooda Recipe By Food Fusion (Ramazan Special)

Falooda|Serves 6-7 |Recipe in English:|Ingredients:|Prepare Falooda Sawaiyan:|-Cornflour Â½ Cup|-Sugar 1 & Â½ tbs|-Water 1 & Â½ Cup|-Ice chilled water|Prepare Quick Rabri:|-Olperâ€™s Milk 2 & Â½ Cups|-Olperâ€™s Dairy Cream 150ml|-Condensed milk Â½ Cup|-Elaichi powder (Cardamom powder) Â¼ tsp|-Vanilla essence Â¼ tsp|-Cornflour 2 tbs|-Olperâ€™s Milk 3-4 tbs|Assembling:|-Tukhme balanga (Basil seeds) soaked in water for 15 minutes |-Lal sharbat |-Falooda sawaiyan|-Mixed nuts sliced|-Green jelly cubes|-Red jelly cubes |-Apple cubes |-Banana slices |-Grapes|-Pineapple chunks |-Prepared strands of noodles are immersed completely in the cold water (use falooda machine or squeeze bottle).|-Let them rest in chilled water with ice cubes & rest it for 10-15 minutes in chilled water & set aside.|Prepare Quick Rabri:|-In a wok,add milk and bring it to boil & cook on medium flame for 2-3 minutes.|-Turn off the flame,add cream & whisk well.|-Turn on the flame,add condensed milk,cardamom & serve!|Recipe in Urdu:|Ajza:|Prepare Falooda Sawaiyan:|-Cornflour Â½ Cup|-Sugar 1 & Â½ tbs|-Water 1 & Â½ Cup|-Ice chilled water|Prepare Quick Rabri:|-Olperâ€™s Milk 2 & Â½ Cups|-Olperâ€™s Dairy for 15 minutes |-Lal sharbat |-Falooda sawaiyan|-Mixed nuts sliced|-Green jelly cubes|-Red jelly cubes |-Apple cubes |-Banana slices |-Grapes|-Pineapple chunks |-Prepared rabri|-Vanilla Ice cornflour mixture ko thanday pani mein squeeze ker lein (use falooda machine or squeeze bottle).|-Noodles strands ko thanday pani mein 10-15 minutes kliya bheego dein & side per rakh dein.|Prepare title: Moskva impact? IAF, Navy join hands with DRDO for CHAFF tech to protect warships, aircraft
description: Amid Russian invasion of Ukraine, the Indian Air Force and the Navy have tied up with the Defence Research Development Organisation to get CHAFF technology. This is in a bid to protect warships from an anti-ship missile during hostilities. India is the second country after the U.S to develop this ability. The development comes as the Indian navy is currently studying the sinking of Russian missile cruiser Moskva. Watch this video to find out more about CHAFF technology.|#IndianAirForce #IndianNavy #DRDO #CHAFF #Russia #Moskva #UkraineWar #Warship #Aircraft

title: Tangis Histeris Pedagang di Bogor Adukan ke Jokowi, Pamannya Ditangkap Polisi karena Tolak Pungli
description: ===|||| JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Dua orang pedagang di salah satu pasar di Bogor histeris saat bertemu dengan Presiden Joko Widodo pada Kamis (21/4)||||Ia juga bercerita kepada Jokowi dan mengadukan bahwa pamannya yang ditangkap polisi karena menolak pungutan liar atau pungli.||||"Pak, Pak Jokowi, Pak tolong kami. Om kami ditangkap polisi. Ditangkap polisi," ujar pedagang kepada Jokowi sambil histeris||||Sontak Presiden dan rombongan pun menghentikan langkahnya, Jokowi pun berusaha menenangkan pedagang tersebut.||||Baca Juga Jokowi Bagikan BLT Minyak Goreng di Pasar Ciawi, Pos Indonesia Capai Penyaluran 95 Persen di https://www.kompas.tv/article/282269/jokowi-bagikan-blt-minyak-goreng-di-pasar-ciawi-pos-indonesia-capai-penyaluran-95-persen||||"Paman kami menolak pungli ditangkap polisi. title: How London became the dirty money capital of the world | FT Film
description: Russian oligarchs and companies have been investing in London for two decades, encouraged by British politicians of all stripes, but critics say the 'London laundromat' cleans dirty money from Russia and across the globe. The FT examines why it took Russia's invasion of Ukraine to put the issue in the spotlight and whether new sanctions and measures to tackle the problem go far enough. Nearly all of the cityâ€™s 25 million residents have been locked in their homes since the start of April and officials say thereâ€™s still no end in sight and restrictions will remain in place. title: Snowfallâ€™s Damson Idris Does His Best Denzel Washington Impression | Ext. Interview | DESUS & MERO
description: We chop it up with actor Damson Idris aka Franklin Saint of FX's "Snowfall" and discuss him learning a South Central accent from rapper WC, being inspired by and working with the late John Singleton, growing up in Peckham, starting out in the theater, being misnomered by Denzel Washington, meeting Idris Elba at Spike Lee's party, being a Lakers fan, his defense of British biscuits, and his advice to those starting out in the industry.|0:00 - Intro|:28 â€“ Season 5 of Snowfall and success of the show|1:05 â€“ Getting the South Central Accent right|2:22 â€“ On working with John Singleton |4:52 â€“ Peckham U.K.|6:08 â€“ On getting his start in theater|7:31 â€“ Denzel Washington Impression|9:00 â€“ On Idris Elbaâ€™s being like a big brother|10:42 â€“ Favorite TV and sports|12:17 â€“ Being inspired by his peers|12:35 â€“ How watching old films helps his acting today|13:16 â€“ On set|14:05 â€“ Favorite British Foods|15:30 â€“ Nigeran restaurants in Peckham, U.K.|16:25 â€“ Where to travel in the U.K.|17:49 â€“ Advice for those starting off in industry|18:14 â€“ Neon sign|#DESUSandMERO |#BodegaHive|#DamsonIdris|Subscribe to the DESUS & MERO YouTube channel: https://goo.gl/MRjgEi|DESUS & MERO, the Bronxâ€™s very own, reconnected online in the early days of Twitter, where they unleashed their potent personalities and found themselves kindred spirits. That led to stints on Complex and MTV, the Bodega Boys podcast, and a daily late-night show on Viceland, developing a feverish following. The quick-witted duo brings a distinct voice to late night, delivering smart and comedic commentary on any and all topics, that keeps audiences buzzing. DESUS & MERO continue to host their Bodega Boys podcast.

title: Otak Pelaku Pemerasan, Oknum Polisi Ditembak
description: ===|||| SEMARANG, KOMPAS.TV - Bripda PPS anggota Polsek Slogohimo Polres Wonogiri, Jawa Tengah, kini masih menjalani perawatan di Rumah Sakit Moewardi Solo karena mengalami luka tembak di bagian perut seblah kiri. Oknum anggota polisi itu diduga menjadi otak pelaku pemerasan terhadap korban WP (60) warga Laweyan Surakarta, Jawa Tengah.||||Aksi pemerasan yang dilakukan oleh oknum angggota polisi bersama dengan empat temannya itu bermula, korban yang dituduh melakukan perzinahan di hotel daerah Sukoharjo kemudian didatangi oleh empat orang dengan membawa bukti foto. Merasa tidak melakukan hal tersebut, korban kemudian melapor ke Polresta Surakarta. ||||Untuk menjebak komplotan pemerasan itu, Tim Resmob bersama dengan korban kemudian melakukan upaya pertemuan dengan menjanjikan uang Rp 14 juta yang dimnta oleh komplotan tersebut.||||Pada saat dilakukan transaksi, petugas kemudian melakukan upaya penangkapan terhadap komplotan itu. Mengetahui ada petugas polisi, komplotan itu melarikan diri menggunakan mobil sambil menyerempet petugas. Petugas kemudian melakukan upaya tembakan ke arah  mobil yang ditumpangi oleh lima orang komplotan tersebut, dan berhasil lolos dari kejaran petugas. Komplotan tersebut kemudian mendatangi rumah sakit di Boyolali untuk memeriksakan salah satu temannya yang terkena tembakan.||||Berhasil mengamankan seorang oknum polisi yang menajdi otak pemerasan, petugas berhasil mengamankan empat temannya berikut barang bukti mobil, senjata api rakitan serta uang hasil pemerasan. ||||Dari hasil penyeldiikan yang dilakukan oleh Polresta Solo, diketahui komplotan ini telah melakukan aksi pemerasan terhadap orang yang keluar dari hotel di wilayah Surakarta, Sukoharjo, Klaten dan Wonogiri. Selain akan menjerat pelaku dengan Pasal 368 KUHP tentang pemerasan, oknum polisi yang menjadi otak pemerasan akan dilakukan pemecatan.||||Hingga kini, oknum anggota Polsek Slogohimo Polres Wonogiri, masih menjalani perawatan di Rumah Sakit Moewardi Solo akibat luka tembak pada bagian perut sebelah kiri.||||#pemerasan #solo #polrestasurakarta|||| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/282303/otak-pelaku-pemerasan-oknum-polisi-ditembak

title: Terror strike in Jammu ahead of PM Modi's visit; CISF officer killed, 2 terrorists eliminated
description: Two days before Prime Minister Narendra Modi's visit, terrorists carried out an attack in Jammu and fired upon a CISF vehicle in Sunjwan area early this morning, killing one paramilitary officer and injuring many others. Soon after the attack, an encounter broke out between the terrorists and security forces in the area during which two insurgents have been gunned down while many security personnel sustained injuries. title: Butaev vs Stanionis HIGHLIGHTS: April 16, 2022 | PBC on Showtime
description: (April 16, 2022) Eimantas Stanionis moved a step closer to establishing himself as one of the sportâ€™s best welterweights with an action-filled split decision win against the rugged Radzhab Butaev, lifting his WBA title in the main event of a special edition of SHOWTIME CHAMPIONSHIP BOXING that preceded the four-fight Spence vs. Ugas SHOWTIME PPVÂ® from AT&T Stadium in Arlington, Texas.| |In a bout fought at close range, Stanionis landed the crisper, more eye-catching shots, repeatedly rocking the sturdy Butaev with hard rights and a reliable jab in the most complete performance of his career. He won by judgesâ€™ scores of 116-111, 117-110 and 113-114, improving to 14-0 with 9 knockouts, while Butaev, who had a point deducted in the 11th for holding and hitting, suffered the first defeat of his career, dropping to 14-1 with 11 knockouts.| |â€œI still canâ€™t believe it,â€ Stanionis said afterward. â€œIt was a dream come true to hear â€˜and the new.â€™ When I was a kid, I visualized what this would look like and how it would feel to become a champion. Itâ€™s because of the hard work, dedication, belief in myself and my team to get me to this big stage. I just want to tell everybody that dreams do come true. If you believe in it and give your everything, it will happen.â€|Displaying a granite chin and impressive punch selection, Stanionis, a 27-year-old former Olympian from Lithuania, made his case for securing a fight with the winner of Saturdayâ€™s main event between IBF/WBC welterweight champion Errol Spence Jr. and WBA champion Yordenis Ugas. |Though Butaev threw 146 more punches than Stanionis, Stanionis landed at a 37% connect rate while Butaevâ€™s connect rate was 19%, according to CompuBox. Stanionis almost quadrupled Butaev in jabs landed 80-21 with Stanionis also landing 42% of his power punches while Butaev landed 29%.|â€œThe fight went like this because the referee allowed Stanionis to fight with his head down the entire time,â€ Butaev said. â€œWhat can I do if the guy is leading with his head down all the time? I donâ€™t know why he took away a point from me. They should have taken the point away from him because he was diving in the whole time.â€|Butaev tried to mix up his attack, switching from southpaw to orthodox, but Stanionis had little trouble solving these different looks.|Stanionis landed a looping overhand right that landed flush in the tenth. But Butaev appeared to buckle Stanionis in the 11th and bloody his nose with a series of blows.|However, moments later Butaev was deducted a point for pushing Stanionisâ€™ head down in a clinch and punching, blunting his momentum.|Butaev made a stand in the last two rounds, pushing Stanionis back with punishing shots but it was Stanionis who, seemingly tiring, answered with two sweeping right hands in the final minute, as the crowd cheered on the action.|The match ended with both men falling to the canvas, winging shots, an appropriate coda to an entertaining brawl. |#EimantasStanionis #RadzhabButaev #ButaevStanionis|Visit PremierBoxingChampions.com for more info.||||SIGN UP FOR FIGHT ALERTS: ||||https://pbcham.ps/FightAlerts||||FOLLOW US:||||https://twitter.com/premierboxing||https://instagram.com/premierboxing||https://www.facebook.com/premierboxingchampions

description: BANJAR, KOMPAS.TV - Area ambruknya minimarket di Kabupaten Banjar, Kalimantan Selatan nampak sepi dibanding sebelumnya pada rabu pagi (20/4/2022).||||Kendati masih ada beberapa warga yang datang melihat lokasi yang sudah di police line dan dijaga pihak kepolisian.||||Baca Juga Menguak Penyebab Minimarket Ambruk di Gambut, Tim Puslabfor Polri Lakukan Penyelidikan di https://www.kompas.tv/article/282259/menguak-penyebab-minimarket-ambruk-di-gambut-tim-puslabfor-polri-lakukan-penyelidikan||||Tak lama, Sa'adah, seorang warga setempat mendatangi polisi untuk melaporkan bahwa dirinya mencium aroma menyengat dari lokasi reruntuhan.||||Aroma tidak sedap tersebut menurutnya muncul dari surut belakang reruntuhan tepat di dekat rumahnya.||||Bagian tersebut menurutnya belum dibongkar oleh tim yang saat itu bekerja.||||Warga menduga aroma mencurigakan tersebut berasal dari mayat atau bangkai, kendati mengaku belum dapat membedakan seperti apa bau bangkai.||||Warga mengaku sudah melaporkan aroma menyengat tersebut ke pihak kepolisian yang berjaga  untuk melakukan tindakan terkait laporan warga.||||"Belum kuat, cuma sudah keluar bau-bau amis, sudah laporan, katanya kan datang hari ini pihak Polda, saya melaporkan karena rumah saya dekat bau itu," ungkap Sa'adah.||||Baca Juga Pemkab Banjar Selidiki Penyebab Ambruknya Minimarket Alfamart Gambut, Dinas PUPR Bentuk Tim di https://www.kompas.tv/article/281896/pemkab-banjar-selidiki-penyebab-ambruknya-minimarket-alfamart-gambut-dinas-pupr-bentuk-tim||||Sementara pencarian korban terjebak reruntuhan telah dihentikan pada selasa sore setelah semua korban yang terdata berhasil ditemukan.||||Kendati demikian pihak petugas menyebut pencarian akan kembali dilakukan jika ada laporan baru kehilangan anggota keluarga dari warga.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/282262/cium-aroma-tidak-sedap-dari-reruntuhan-minimarket-ambruk-warga-sempat-curiga-masih-ada-korban

title: Ministerial Roundtable Discussion for Support to Ukraine | WBG-IMF Spring Meetings 2022
description: The war in Ukraine is having a devastating impact on the countryâ€™s economy. The World Bank estimates that Ukraineâ€™s economy will shrink by almost half this year, trade has largely halted, and the countryâ€™s infrastructure has sustained heavy damage. In addition, there is a large humanitarian crisis â€“ an estimated 5 million people, about half of whom are children, have become refugees in other countries, and another 7.1 million people have been displaced internally (UNHCR estimates). The war has dramatically impacted the Government of Ukraineâ€™s ability to sustain essential government services, provide for social protection and humanitarian needs, and make critical time-sensitive investments. The World Bank Group and the Government of Ukraine convened a roundtable discussion to better understand the scope of Ukraineâ€™s immediate financing needs, and to discuss how the international community can come together to support those needs. Complicating matters and threatening the mission is the arrival of Zurg, an imposing presence with an army of ruthless robots and a mysterious agenda. title: THE BAD GUYS | First 6 Minutes
description: Nobody has ever failed so hard at trying to be good as The Bad Guys.|In the new action comedy from DreamWorks Animation, based on the New York Times best-selling book series, a crackerjack criminal crew of animal outlaws are about to attempt their most challenging con yetâ€”becoming model citizens. |Never have there been five friends as infamous as The Bad Guysâ€”dashing pickpocket Mr. Wolf (Academy AwardÂ® winner Sam Rockwell, Three Billboards Outside Ebbing, Missouri), seen-it-all safecracker Mr. Snake (Marc Maron, GLOW), chill master-of-disguise Mr. Shark (Craig Robinson, Hot Tub Time Machine franchise), short-fused â€œmuscleâ€ Mr. Piranha (Anthony Ramos, In the Heights) and sharp-tongued expert hacker Ms. Tarantula (Awkwafina, Crazy Rich Asians), aka â€œWebs.â€ |But when, after years of countless heists and being the worldâ€™s most-wanted villains, the gang is finally caught, Mr. Wolf brokers a deal (that he has no intention of keeping) to save them all from prison: The Bad Guys will go good. |Under the tutelage of their mentor Professor Marmalade (Richard Ayoade, Paddington 2), an arrogant (but adorable!) guinea pig, The Bad Guys set out to fool the world that theyâ€™ve been transformed. Along the way, though, Mr. Wolf begins to suspect that doing good for real may give him what heâ€™s always secretly longed for: acceptance. title: 1,000HP ATTACK! First Nurburgring Laps in My Ferrari SF90 Stradale | WHERE'S SHMEE Part 21
description: My new Ferrari SF90 Stradale at the NÃ¼rburgring, and it's every bit as fast as you'd think for a 1,000hp supercar! However, after the recent issues with the sound of my STO, let's start this one off for a lap under EV power, before we dial it all up!|After getting my Lamborghini Huracan STO out for a first lap on the Green Hell, this time around it's the turn of my very recently collected Ferrari SF90 Stradale. In fact the car is so new, it's not actually even been home yet before completing some laps of the NÃ¼rburgring Nordschleife!|However, first up, with full charge in the battery pack I'm curious to see how it fares attempting to get as far as possible around the lap under electric power as possible, and in doing so being a front-wheel drive Ferrari in the process. It turns out the expected 25km range runs out very quickly when you're pushing to the 141km/h (87mph) Vmax in the eD setting. All is not lost though, because as soon as the 4.0l TT V8 fires up, all 1,000hp are instantly available it's time for a crazy ride.|Like all new Shmeemobiles, it's a rite of passage to head out onto this famous loop and during Touristenfahrten (Tourist Drives) as a public toll road with normal road rules during Easter Weekend, we have a great opportunity to enjoy it properly. This time around thankfully, no sound limits are being pushed, so it's all good to have a lot of fun.|Awesome thumbnail pic from SAJU Pictures, be sure to check out pics of your laps and GP sessions at RaceTracker.de as well!|https://www.racetracker.de|Thanks for watching, Tim||||Chapters:|00:00 Intro|00:45 Track Prep|05:07 First Nurburgring Lap in EV|10:36 Second Nurburgring Lap with 1,000hp|15:39 Final Thoughts|17:49 Wrap Up|#Ferrari #Nurburgring #WheresShmee|Subscribe: http://bit.ly/Shmee150YT||Website: http://www.shmee150.com||Shop: http://shop.shmee150.com||Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/shmee150||Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/shmee150

title: Judika feat. Nurlela - Tak Pernah Tinggalkanku (Official Music Video)
description: #Judika #TakPernahTinggalkanku #JudikaXNurlela|Judika kini baru saja mengeluarkan lagu duet pertama selain bersama istrinya di Indonesia, yakni bersama Nurlela, penyandang disabilitas netra yang memiliki kemampuan bernyanyi dari Panti Sosial Rehabilitasi Penyandang Disabilitas (PSRPD). Lagu duet Judika dengan Nurlela yang berjudul â€œTak pernah tinggalkan kuâ€ rilis pada tanggal 21 April 2022, dimana dalam video clip musik tersebut juga diperankan oleh Menteri BUMN, bapak Erick Thohir.|Judika menyatakan â€œNurlela memiliki suara yang berkarakterâ€. Diketahui bahwa sedari kecil Nurlela memiliki hobi mendengarkan dan menyanyikan lagu dangdut, namun kini ia mencoba untuk menyanyikan lagu pop. Menurut Judika, hal itu lah yang membuat suaranya terdengar spesial. Dalam interviewnya, Nurlela mengatakan bahwa pada mulanya ia kurang menyukai lagu pop, namun semenjak mendengar lagu Judika â€˜Jikalau kau cintaâ€™ yaitu lagu pop pertama yang ia dengar, ia tersentuh dan pikirannya mulai terbuka untuk memperdalam musik pop.|Dalam suatu kunjungan pada bulan Oktober 2021, Menteri BUMN, bapak Erick Thohir, di PSRPD Cimahi, Nurlela menunjukan bakatnya dan menyatakan bahwa ia mengidolakan Judika. Hal tersebut ditanggapi dengan baik oleh bapak Erick Thohir dan segera ingin mewujudkan mimpi Nurlela dengan memberikan kejutan pertemuan dengan sang idola.|Pada pertemuan Judika dan Nurlela di kantor Kementerian BUMN, Judika merasa hatinya tergerak dan spontan mengatakan â€œyuk kita bikin single duetâ€ pada Nurlela. Ajakan tersebut diterima dengan antusias oleh Nurlela. Menurut Judika, banyak orang disabilitas yang terampil dan memiliki kemampuan tak terbatas namun karena disabilitas fisik, kesempatan itu jadi terbatas. title: Putin tells forces to seal off last Mariupol fighters - BBC News
